    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Acquired/Inherited Template</strong>&nbsp;Acquired<br><strong>Simple Template</strong>&nbsp;Yes<br><strong>Usable with Summons</strong>&nbsp;Yes - Requires the feat Versatile Summon Monster or Versatile Summon Nature's Ally<br><br>Fiery creatures are native denizens of the Elemental Planes of Fire, and act as conduits to the burning energies of their home plane. This template can be applied only to a non-outsider that has none of the following subtypes: air, cold, earth, fire, or water. Creatures with a swim speed can’t be fiery creatures. A fiery creature’s CR increases by 1 only if the base creature has 5 or more HD.<br><br><strong>Rebuild Rules:</strong>&nbsp;Type&nbsp;gains the fire subtype;&nbsp;Senses&nbsp;gains darkvision 60 ft.;&nbsp;Defensive Abilities&nbsp;gains DR as noted on the table below;&nbsp;Attacks&nbsp;gains bonus fire damage as noted on the table below on attacks with natural weapons and metal weapons.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<hr>\n<table class=\"inner\" style=\"border-color: white; color: #ffffff; font-family: 'Century Gothic', CenturyGothic, AppleGothic, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: #0f0f0f;\">\n<tbody style=\"margin-top: 0px;\">\n<tr style=\"margin-top: 0px;\">\n<td style=\"margin: 0px; border: 1px solid white; padding: 1px 5px; text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"margin-top: 0px;\">Hit Dice</strong></td>\n<td style=\"border: 1px solid white; padding: 1px 5px; margin: 0px; text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"margin-top: 0px;\">DR</strong></td>\n<td style=\"border: 1px solid white; padding: 1px 5px; margin: 0px; text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"margin-top: 0px;\">Fire Damage</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"background: #3e3e3e;\">\n<td style=\"margin: 0px; border: 1px solid white; padding: 1px 5px; text-align: center;\">1-4</td>\n<td style=\"border: 1px solid white; padding: 1px 5px; margin: 0px; text-align: center;\">-</td>\n<td style=\"border: 1px solid white; padding: 1px 5px; margin: 0px; t